                    <h1>Gustavo Dore (1832–1883)</h1>

        <table>
                <tr>
                        <td><img src="imgs/forthwithUprightHeRearsFromOffThePoolHisMightyStature.jpg" alt="" width="200" height="265"><br><p>"Forthwith Upright"</p></td>
                    
